U.K. Stocks Pare Losses; Benchmark FTSE 100 Is Little Changed

-- B y   W i l l   H a d f i e l d
-- 
2011-12-09T08:27:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-09/ftse-100-stocks-pare-losses-benchmark-ftse-100-index-is-little-changed.html
U.K. stocks pared losses, following
two days of declines, as  BG Group Plc (BG/)  and  Vodafone Group Plc (VOD) 
rebounded, offsetting a slide by  Aviva Plc. (AV/)   The benchmark FTSE 100 Index slid 0.1 percent to 5,480.28
at 8:25 a.m. in London after earlier dropping as much as 0.8
percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
